<paragraph blockId="3.[94,643,888,1040]" pageId="3">
<emphasis box="[94,402,888,912]" italics="true" pageId="3">
Discussão: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Martins &amp; Galileo" authorityYear="2008" box="[200,402,888,912]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Pyrianoreina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hovorei" status="sp. nov.">Pyrianoreina hovorei</taxonomicName>
